msgstr "Zu Veranstaltung einladen"

#: js/invite-resource.js
msgid "de.systopia.eventinvitation"
msgstr ""

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Settings.hlp
msgid "Here you can enable the use of an external registration-page."
msgstr ""
"Hier können Sie die Verwendung einer externen Registrierungs-Seite "
"aktivieren."

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Settings.hlp
msgid ""
"If this box is not checked but a url has been provided, then that url will "
"be ignored and the built-in registration-page will be used."
msgstr ""

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Settings.hlp
msgid ""
"Here you can add a url, in order to use an external registration-page, "
"rather than the built-in one."
msgstr ""

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Settings.hlp
msgid ""
"The provided url <strong>has to</strong> contain the <code>&#123;token&#125;"
"</code> which will be replaced by the generated code."
msgstr ""
"Die bereitgestellte URL <strong>muss</strong> den <code>&#123;token&#125;</"
"code> enthalten, der durch den generierten Code ersetzt wird."

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Settings.hlp
msgid "Here you can define, until when the token should be valid."
msgstr ""

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Settings.hlp
msgid ""
"After the event has ended, none of the tokens will be valid any more, "
"regardless of this setting."
msgstr ""

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Settings.hlp
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that this is encoded in the token itself, so changing this "
"setting will only affect newly generated tokens."
msgstr ""

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Task/ContactSearch.hlp
msgid ""
"The template chosen here <strong>must</strong> contain the <code>&#123;"
"$qr_event_invite_code&#125;</code> token. It contains the personalised "
"invitation link."
msgstr ""
"Die gewählte Vorlage <strong>muss</strong> den Token <code>&#123;"
"$qr_event_invite_code&#125;</code> enthalten. Dieser enthält den "
"personalisierten Link."

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Task/ContactSearch.hlp
msgid "Beyond that, the following special tokens are available:"
msgstr "Darüber hinaus sind die folgenden Zusatztoken verfügbar:"

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Task/ContactSearch.hlp
msgid ""
"<code>&#123;$event.xxx&#125;</code>: fields of the given event. For the "
"available 'xxx' field names, check the API explorer with <code>Event.get</"
"code>."
msgstr ""
"<code>&#123;$event.xxx&#125;</code>: Informationen der Veranstaltung. Eine "
"List der verfügbaren 'xxx' Felder können Sie über den API Explorer über "
"<code>Event.get</code> erhalten."

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Task/ContactSearch.hlp
msgid ""
"<code>&#123;$qr_event_invite_code_data&#125;</code>: QR-Code date to be used "
"in as <code>src</code> in an html <code>img</code> tag."
msgstr ""
"<code>&#123;$qr_event_invite_code_data&#125;</code>: QR-Code Daten, die als "
"<code>src</code> Feld ein einem HTML <code>img</code> Tag verwendet werden "
"können."

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Task/ContactSearch.hlp
msgid ""
"<code>&#123;$qr_event_invite_code_img&#125;</code>: QR-Code <code>img</code> "
"element."
msgstr ""
"<code>&#123;$qr_event_invite_code_img&#125;</code>: QR-Code als HTML "
"<code>img</code> Element."

#: templates/CRM/Eventinvitation/Form/Task/ContactSearch.tpl
msgid ""
"For inviting contacts as resources for the selected event, select the role "
"%1 and choose the resource demand they should be assigned to."
msgstr ""

